languages.text: "Жив и здравствует, Ваша Светлость. Думаю, скоро вы сами в этом убедитесь. И отдельно благодарю вас за то, что так любезно предоставили в его распоряжение свой шаттл. Инквизиция ценит помощь истинно верующих чад Императора".

traits.locale_text: "Жив и здравствует, Ваша милость. Думаю, скоро вы сами в этом убедитесь. И отдельно благодарю вас за то, что так любезно предоставили в его распоряжение свой шаттл. Инквизиция ценит помощь истинно верующих чад Императора".

languages.text: "He is alive and well, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I imagine you will see for yourself soon. And please accept my gratitude for being so kind as to lend him your shuttle. The Inquisition values the assistance of the truly faithful children of the Emperor."

languages.text: 「彼は健在です、陛下。すぐにその目で確認できるでしょう。陛下のシャトルに派遣させていただける、そのご厚意に感謝いたします。皇帝に心からの忠誠を誓う子らを助けることが重要だと、異端審問庁は考えております」
languages.original_text: "He is alive and well, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I imagine you will see for yourself soon. And please accept my gratitude for being so kind as to lend him your shuttle. The Inquisition values the assistance of the truly faithful children of the Emperor."

languages.text: “他安然无恙，大人。我相信，你很快就能亲眼见到他了。请接受我的谢意，感谢你把你的穿梭机借给了他。你协助了帝皇的忠实子民，我们审判庭非常看重这样的协助。”
languages.original_text: "He is alive and well, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I imagine you will see for yourself soon. And please accept my gratitude for being so kind as to lend him your shuttle. The Inquisition values the assistance of the truly faithful children of the Emperor."

languages.text: «Está vivo y sano, mi{mf|lord|lady}. Imagino que pronto lo verá con sus propios ojos. Ah, y acepte mi agradecimiento por prestarle amablemente una lanzadera. La Inquisición agradece la ayuda de los hijos fieles del Emperador».
languages.original_text: "He is alive and well, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I imagine you will see for yourself soon. And please accept my gratitude for being so kind as to lend him your shuttle. The Inquisition values the assistance of the truly faithful children of the Emperor."

languages.text: « Il est sain et sauf, Votre Seigneurie. Vous devriez pouvoir le constater par vous-même très bientôt. Permettez-moi de vous remercier d'avoir eu la bonté de lui prêter votre navette. L'Inquisition sait apprécier à sa juste valeur l'aide des véritables fidèles de l'Empereur. »
languages.original_text: "He is alive and well, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. I imagine you will see for yourself soon. And please accept my gratitude for being so kind as to lend him your shuttle. The Inquisition values the assistance of the truly faithful children of the Emperor."

languages.text: "Er ist am Leben und bei guter Gesundheit, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Ihr werdet das in Kürze selbst feststellen können. Und bitte nehmt meinen Dank dafür entgegen, dass Ihr ihm Euer Shuttle geliehen habt. Die Inquisition weiß die Unterstützung wahrhaft gläubiger Kinder des Imperators zu schätzen."

languages.text: "Kendisi sağ salim aramızda {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Herhâlde yakında bizzat görürsün. Ayrıca büyük bir incelik yapıp ona mekiğini ödünç verdiğin için sana teşekkürü borç bilirim. Engizisyon, İmparator'un gerçekten inançlı evlatlarının desteğini takdir ediyor."

traits.locale_text: "Kendisi sağ salim aramızda {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Herhalde yakında onu kendiniz de görürsünüz. Ayrıca büyük bir incelik yapıp ona mekiğinizi ödünç verdiğiniz için de size teşekkürü bir borç bilirim. Engizisyon, İmparator'un gerçekten inançlı evlatlarının desteğini takdir ediyor."
